WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:03.130
Hey, good morning family, how are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.130 --> 00:00:07.906
Well, I have some things on my heart that the Lord has shown me, and I'm excited about this.

00:00:07.906 --> 00:00:21.840
He started talking to me about the outpouring of His Spirit again—a major change coming, a major—I'm going to say it's like the tipping of the waterfall again.

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:44.253
And the things that the Lord is talking to me about, I saw a door, a massive door, and it was a white door, a beautiful painted white door, but on this door there was purple, there were swirls of different—like the glory of what I want to call the Shekinah Glory.

00:00:44.253 --> 00:00:49.640
It looked like mist, and it was covering this door, but it was beautiful.

00:00:49.640 --> 00:00:54.342
The colors, the pinks and stuff, the clouds are in front of it and behind.

00:00:54.342 --> 00:01:00.399
In the door frame behind the door was like a dimension.

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:12.479
Okay, and in that dimension behind it was the glory, and I could see the light coming through the cracks of the door.

00:01:12.789 --> 00:01:23.302
It was shining through that door on the cracks, and I could see like it was just trying to bust through—the glory of God was trying to bust through this door.

00:01:23.302 --> 00:01:28.404
And behind it was the same, which was amazing.

00:01:28.404 --> 00:01:32.025
I don't know how else to describe this.

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:39.884
Behind it was the same dimension as the front side, but it was like a door that was standing all alone, but it was a door that you could open up to it.

00:01:42.695 --> 00:01:57.512
And I had to say it like this, but this is a way I can try—I'm trying to paint a picture for y'all like The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe, how there was a closet and they walked through the closet and they could go through the other dimension into Narnia.

00:01:58.119 --> 00:02:00.612
So that's kind of like what I saw.

00:02:00.612 --> 00:02:09.813
It was a door that was like a passage, but on the other side of it, without opening the door, He was walking through the dimension.

00:02:09.813 --> 00:02:16.428
It was still in the same dimension because on this side I could see the pink and all the beautiful stuff again.

00:02:16.428 --> 00:02:27.462
But the Lord said to me, 'Everything is about to change, for in this space of time you've hit this where we are.

00:02:27.462 --> 00:02:30.560
' Help me, Holy Spirit.

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:34.662
He said, 'This dispensation of time is coming to an end.

00:02:34.662 --> 00:02:39.560
' That's what He was saying to me and where we are in it.

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:44.640
And I saw Adam's lease coming up again.

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:51.284
It was up, and we were going into another space of time.

00:02:51.284 --> 00:03:12.987
And He said to me, during Rosh Hashanah this week—this week is an amazing week because this is the beginning on the second, which is in two days, the beginning of Rosh Hashanah, which goes into the third and I believe the fourth, at whenever the new moon and all that is.

00:03:12.987 --> 00:03:19.200
I believe—I'm not going to quote right because I am not a Jewish scholar—but I'm just saying this is what I've seen.

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:43.670
So He said, 'This time frame is the beginning of the new creative miracles, that we have hit a time and space that we've hit a time in history where Adam's lease is coming up, that we are getting ready for the great outpouring and we're going home.

00:03:43.670 --> 00:03:46.010
' We're getting ready to go home.

00:03:46.010 --> 00:03:52.160
I saw the glory behind this door and I saw the door was going to open.

00:03:52.160 --> 00:03:56.864
And He said, 'In a 24-hour period, everything will change.

00:03:56.864 --> 00:04:07.164
Everything that you know, everything that you've ever known up until this point in human history, everything will change like a light switch.

00:04:07.164 --> 00:04:10.589
' He said, 'Brandon, it's going to be like a light switch that flips on.

00:04:10.589 --> 00:04:21.280
' He said that time frame is coming to an end, what we've seen, and He said, 'You're coming into a new time frame, and you're going to cross and you're going to go through this door.

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:31.050
' And I saw the glory again upon the bride, upon the body, in a way that is huge.

00:04:31.495 --> 00:04:44.067
We think we've seen stuff in the past—revivals, demonstrations, and manifestations of the glory, outpourings of when Azusa Street happened.

00:04:44.067 --> 00:05:03.849
You know, there was a prophetic word that was given over a hundred years ago now that said that there would be another revival like Azusa in a hundred years that would be bigger than what happened at Azusa, and it's been going on 120-some years now.

00:05:03.849 --> 00:05:09.347
But He said they didn't quite say it was going to be a hundred years, it would be in a hundred-year time frame.

00:05:09.347 --> 00:05:11.590
Well, we're in 120 years.

00:05:11.590 --> 00:05:17.893
In two years, I believe, we're in that time frame of that prophetic word that was given.

00:05:17.893 --> 00:05:20.595
So here we are at the last of the last.

00:05:21.660 --> 00:05:30.939
I'm telling you all, Jesus is coming and the sun is going down on this dispensation of grace.

00:05:30.939 --> 00:05:37.733
And I saw the devil petitioning again for his seven-year tribulation.

00:05:37.733 --> 00:05:42.299
And I saw he had a—this time he had a black cloak on.

00:05:42.299 --> 00:05:49.565
It was a massive black cloak, and he was moving around very sneaky and just evil, the way he was moving.

00:05:49.565 --> 00:05:57.639
And he is lurching around, kind of like Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs whenever that old witch was there and she had that black cloak on.

00:05:57.639 --> 00:05:59.463
That's the way the devil looked.

00:05:59.463 --> 00:06:13.440
But he was going and I saw him go and he was talking to the Pope, which I think is just a wow, but he was talking to the Pope, influencing the Vatican and the church in Rome.

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:16.400
Because I was like, 'What is that all about?

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:23.106
' But I saw the devil trying to go and influence and talk to the Pope in the Vatican and he was speaking to him.

00:06:23.106 --> 00:06:26.533
I don't even know if the Pope knew he was being talked to, but he was.

00:06:26.839 --> 00:06:34.714
He was talking to the Pope, and I saw the Pope and he had his white beanie on—his head thing—and he was looking down.

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:41.978
But the devils were standing behind him trying to influence him, talking to him.

00:06:43.351 --> 00:06:54.156
And then I saw Italy and I saw cracks all in the soil again with like lava and fire all over Italy again.

00:06:54.156 --> 00:06:59.480
I saw fire and it was like the earth was splitting, like from an earthquake, remember?

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:11.874
And I warned you all about a volcano that the Lord told me to intercede in behalf of Italy, that there would be a lot of people perish because of a tsunami in the water and because of volcanic activity.

00:07:11.874 --> 00:07:13.835
I told you this about a year ago.

00:07:13.835 --> 00:07:20.674
And when I was interceding, I saw the angels coming out of the sky and they were warning the people and waking them up.

00:07:20.674 --> 00:07:25.026
And there was a mist, like a canary in the coal mine.

00:07:25.026 --> 00:07:32.720
I told you all about the canary in the coal mine and it was on the perch and it fell over dead, and there was a gas coming up out of the ground.

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:40.204
And I saw like a mist, a fog over the land over this town in Italy, and it was on the coastline.

00:07:40.204 --> 00:07:45.427
And the angels were warning the people and they were coming out, and I saw a portal open up over Italy.

00:07:49.254 --> 00:08:00.708
If anybody who's followed this channel for a while remembers this, that I warned about this and we were interceding for Italy that this major earthquake would not take place and destroy a lot of people.

00:08:00.708 --> 00:08:02.650
I saw 300,000 people perish.

00:08:02.650 --> 00:08:07.048
And so I saw that again.

00:08:07.048 --> 00:08:14.455
I saw Italy splitting open, I saw fire coming up out of these cracks, and I thought it was interesting.

00:08:14.455 --> 00:08:22.396
But I saw the Pope being influenced by a demon, by the devil, and he was talking to the devil.

00:08:22.396 --> 00:08:37.279
And so I saw in this time frame where we are in eternity and the Lord was telling me, He said, 'Brandon, we are at that sliver of time.

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:47.040
' And He said, 'And you know when the Bible says a day is a thousand years to the Lord, a thousand years is as a day, right?

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:58.387
' So I saw thousand, thousand, thousand, thousand—clear to the beginning of time the Lord showed me.

00:08:58.387 --> 00:09:10.617
And I'm telling you, I had an experience of the Lord beyond anything I've been able to ever tell you all, and I've told you all some amazing experiences.

00:09:10.617 --> 00:09:19.080
But this experience that I had with the Lord was beyond anything I've ever seen before.

00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:23.152
It was like—to say it shook me—it was beyond saying it.

00:09:25.627 --> 00:09:29.191
My son and my wife, they recorded it; they were here for it.

00:09:29.191 --> 00:09:41.800
And I'm not going to go into a lot of it because a lot of the word that was given when I had this visitation about four or five days ago was so intense because He was speaking to me directly.

00:09:41.800 --> 00:09:46.200
And so a lot of it is not for the public.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:10:07.640
But in this, He showed me Adam's lease, He showed me the door like I'm talking about, He showed me where we are in time again, and He took time on a thin line, a thread, and He spread it out by every thousand years.

00:10:07.640 --> 00:10:18.255
And He took me through time and it was way out there, but I could see from the beginning whenever He spoke the world into existence.

00:10:18.255 --> 00:10:22.640
I saw Adam walking the earth, I saw Noah and the flood.

00:10:22.640 --> 00:10:26.826
He took me to each one and how they were milestones in history.

00:10:26.826 --> 00:10:36.555
And I saw each thing, from the Roman Empire to the Ottoman Empire, He showed it to me.

00:10:36.555 --> 00:10:44.988
But each thing was divided up into a thousand years, and then a thousand years would divide up into a hundred years, and then it went down to ten years, to a decade.

00:10:44.988 --> 00:10:47.714
And He showed it out, it was on a timeline.

00:10:47.714 --> 00:10:56.085
And He took me through the timeline in space with Him, traveling to where we are right now, ladies and gentlemen.

00:10:56.085 --> 00:11:07.960
And I'm telling you, Jesus Christ is getting ready to come back, and He's coming back for not a busted and disgusted church, He's coming back for a glorious church.

00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:11.399
He's coming back for a church that's on fire for Him.

00:11:11.399 --> 00:11:14.494
He is looking and yearning for His bride.

00:11:14.494 --> 00:11:26.880
And I'm telling you, it's time to get more serious than you've ever been before, for where we are in time—time is up, one last call.

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:34.745
He said, 'Remember, where we are right now,' He said, 'Brandon, I can control time.

00:11:34.745 --> 00:11:53.589
' And He showed me where Adam's lease and everything was up, but there was a sliver right here in between, like a couple of seconds, like a couple minutes—you know what I'm saying—like it was a long enough time for Him to have His revival and be able to bring in a harvest of souls.

00:11:53.589 --> 00:11:58.266
He said, 'Because I have never been defeated nor will I ever be.

00:11:58.266 --> 00:12:08.632
' He said, 'I will not allow you to run back and be afraid of what the devil is doing.

00:12:08.632 --> 00:12:16.422
' He said, 'You are to put on your armor and be strong in the Lord in the power of His might.

00:12:16.422 --> 00:12:19.568
' It's time for us to be like the Davids.

00:12:19.568 --> 00:12:25.789
And He said, 'There's a lot of people, Brandon, that are tired—the older generation, they're tired and they're ready to come home.

00:12:25.789 --> 00:12:28.013
' And He said, 'Allow that to happen.

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:35.133
If they're ready and they want to come home and they're satisfied, they can come on home.

00:12:35.133 --> 00:12:37.960
But I will not allow my church to be defeated.

00:12:37.960 --> 00:12:41.334
' He said, 'They will be victorious on the way out.

00:12:41.334 --> 00:12:46.785
' He said, 'The seeds that you've sowed in the past will come to harvest at last.

00:12:46.785 --> 00:12:52.937
' And He said, 'That's not even about the bad seeds, Brandon, that the wicked have sowed.

00:12:52.937 --> 00:12:55.693
' He said, 'I'm a God of the harvest.

00:12:55.693 --> 00:13:01.889
I'm going to bring in financial harvest beyond anything you can comprehend.

00:13:01.889 --> 00:13:04.935
There will be decamillionaires in the near future.

00:13:04.935 --> 00:13:17.582
' He said, 'Brandon, there will be a transfer of the wealth from the wicked like it was when the children of Israel left Egypt.

00:13:17.582 --> 00:13:27.040
' He said, 'I will bring forth a harvest of finances on my children as a sign and a wonder in these last days.

00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:32.731
' I saw a group of people rising up that were—and I didn't even know what the word decamillionaire was.

00:13:32.731 --> 00:13:40.080
I'm telling y'all, I'm not a real educated person, and I had told my wife, 'This is what the Lord used.

00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:42.960
' I said, 'He said decamillionaire.

00:13:42.960 --> 00:13:44.399
What is a decamillionaire?

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:47.342
' I said, 'Can we Google it?

00:13:47.342 --> 00:13:52.451
' So she Googled it and said, 'Honey, it's above ten million dollars.

00:13:52.451 --> 00:14:07.889
' Anybody who has above a ten million dollar—the Lord said that there is tons of seed in the ground that's coming to pass and there's harvest that's coming for His bright people.

00:14:11.755 --> 00:14:17.839
He has not forgotten those seeds; those seeds have lied dormant in the ground and they're going to spring forth now.

00:14:34.969 --> 00:14:35.324
It's time for the seeds that you sowed—financial, sacrificial seeds—that God said, 'I'm going to breathe on those seeds and I'm going to bring a harvest to you now.

00:14:35.324 --> 00:14:36.400
' It's time.

00:14:36.400 --> 00:14:41.898
He said, 'Brandon, do not let go of the seeds you've sacrificially sowed.

00:14:53.498 --> 00:14:53.636
Do not let go of the sacrificial time that you've given.

00:14:53.636 --> 00:15:00.943
' He said, 'Brandon, I'm bringing forth great joy, I'm bringing forth great harvest.

00:15:00.943 --> 00:15:04.850
' He said, 'Days of Heaven on Earth, fun days are coming for my body.

00:15:04.850 --> 00:15:07.200
It's not a time to be woe-is-me.

00:15:07.200 --> 00:15:10.199
Oh gosh, we got to go and hide in the caves.

00:15:10.199 --> 00:15:18.600
It's time to rise and shine for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen upon you.

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:24.136
' And I'm telling you, the Lord showed me a financial harvest.

00:15:24.136 --> 00:15:31.088
People ask, 'Why do we need that if we're going to heaven?

00:15:31.088 --> 00:15:38.280
' If you don't want yours, I'll take it for you.

00:15:47.319 --> 00:15:50.251
If you don't want your financial harvest and what God's wanting to do for you, that's fine; just put it all over there and give it to somebody who will use it for Him.

00:15:51.554 --> 00:15:59.276
You know, people get all bent out of shape, 'Well, I don't want to do—I want to just go to heaven.

00:15:59.276 --> 00:16:01.480
' We're going to go victorious.

00:16:01.480 --> 00:16:04.680
We're going to go with our heads held high.

00:16:04.680 --> 00:16:07.160
We're not cowering down because the devil's taking ground.

00:16:09.182 --> 00:16:13.839
He said, 'Brandon, the problem is that the body of Christ has been off-kilter.

00:16:13.839 --> 00:16:23.502
' He said, 'They've tried to demasculinize the men of the church by making them metrosexual, feminine like'—He called them limp-wristed.

00:16:25.257 --> 00:16:32.222
He said, 'It's time for my men to get a backbone like David did in the Bible, and they're mighty men of war.

00:16:32.222 --> 00:16:38.536
' And He said, 'If you want to take the land, son, you've got to have some testosterone to you.

00:16:38.536 --> 00:16:40.560
You've got to have some manpower behind you.

00:16:40.560 --> 00:16:44.433
You can't be this passive, seeker-friendly—well, you know, whatever will be, will be.

00:16:44.433 --> 00:16:49.613
' He said, 'You've got to be a warrior in the Kingdom.

00:16:49.613 --> 00:16:57.060
You've got to take your sword and your shield like David did and go and take the land.

00:16:57.060 --> 00:17:02.600
' You know, He showed me, He said how it was with Moses.

00:17:02.600 --> 00:17:17.720
They said to Joshua and Caleb, 'The giants make us like grasshoppers,' and they had a whole generation die off before they were able to do something.

00:17:25.440 --> 00:17:25.840
And He said, 'Brandon, if I have to do that again, I can do it.

00:17:25.840 --> 00:17:38.400
But I know there is a generation—I'm talking about us—we're not going to have to pass it and let a lot of people go home like they did in forty years.

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:42.839
We don't have forty years, ladies and gentlemen.

00:17:42.839 --> 00:17:44.906
Jesus is coming.

00:17:44.906 --> 00:18:01.720
' But it was just an illustration of what He's talking about—raising up Davids, raising up the ones that would take the land and taking the land back for Him, being bold about our faith, being bold about laying hands on the sick and casting out devils.

00:18:01.720 --> 00:18:09.973
Freely we've been given, freely we give it out, sharing the good news with the people for this last harvest.

00:18:09.973 --> 00:18:22.070
And if Jesus Christ could come back tomorrow, I'm just saying—you know, I'm always expecting—but go with your head held high, go with a fight to you, have a backbone about who you are and take the land for Jesus.

00:18:34.599 --> 00:18:34.919
That's what I'm talking about.

00:18:34.919 --> 00:18:41.000
And that's what He showed me, that He never designed us for fear.

00:18:52.476 --> 00:18:52.768
And He said to me, 'Where in my word have you ever heard me tell you to be afraid of what's coming?

00:18:52.768 --> 00:18:54.520
' He said, 'Never.

00:18:54.520 --> 00:19:01.827
' In Joshua 1:9, He said to me, 'Be strong and of good courage, for I the Lord your God am with you wherever you go.

00:19:01.827 --> 00:19:09.340
' Now, I may have not said that exactly right, but you can look it up yourself.

00:19:09.340 --> 00:19:16.496
But I'm just saying, He was saying, 'I want you not to be afraid.

00:19:16.496 --> 00:19:28.251
' He said, 'Brandon, there is a shaking coming, there is a storm that is coming upon your shores, and it will shake everything that you've ever known, ladies and gentlemen.

00:19:28.251 --> 00:19:32.180
It will change within a 24-hour period.

00:19:32.180 --> 00:19:36.370
It's going to change and it will be that quick of a change.

00:19:36.370 --> 00:19:38.850
It would be like a light switch being flipped on.

00:19:38.850 --> 00:19:42.270
' He said it would be bigger than 9/11.

00:19:42.270 --> 00:19:46.035
It's going to be such a humongous event that will change everything that quick.

00:19:57.280 --> 00:19:59.920
But He started talking to me about not being afraid.

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:01.520
He said, 'That's not your focus.

00:20:01.520 --> 00:20:02.827
Your focus is off.

00:20:02.827 --> 00:20:04.500
You're focusing on the storm.

00:20:04.500 --> 00:20:06.742
You're focusing too much on what's coming.

00:20:06.742 --> 00:20:26.129
' He said, because I was asking Him—I was praying, you know, getting off in the flesh—and I was like, 'Oh Lord, I'm praying for the election, praying for Donald Trump, praying for this stuff, and oh God, you know what happens if the people don't get out and vote?

00:20:26.129 --> 00:20:29.919
' And I was just worrying and fretting about it.

00:20:36.620 --> 00:20:36.840
He said, 'Brandon, Brandon, Brandon, I've got this.

00:20:36.840 --> 00:20:37.720
I've got this.

00:20:37.720 --> 00:20:38.484
Like, chill, dude.

00:20:38.484 --> 00:20:45.947
' And I'm like, you know, in my heart I'm going, 'The sky is falling, I've got to pray for the nation America.

00:20:45.947 --> 00:20:48.553
' That's why He's like, 'Chill, chill, Brandon.

00:20:48.553 --> 00:20:49.293
I've got this.

00:20:49.293 --> 00:20:50.800
' Ladies and gentlemen, He's got this.

00:20:52.733 --> 00:21:02.176
The sky isn't falling even though we look at all the stuff going on around us and we think, 'Well, Lord, do you not see all the things going on?

00:21:02.176 --> 00:21:03.982
' Israel's at war.

00:21:07.640 --> 00:21:07.876
He showed me major war breaking out in Europe again.

00:21:11.249 --> 00:21:18.436
I saw a major thing happening in Europe and He told me, 'This is going to be coming, you need to pray over this.

00:21:18.436 --> 00:21:23.947
' And I prayed over it, you know, about the war escalating in Europe.

00:21:26.767 --> 00:21:33.504
And He's just warning me about these things that I'm telling you all about, but He said, 'Where is it ever to be afraid about any of it?

00:21:33.504 --> 00:21:48.510
' It's not for you to ever hide in a hole about it; it's for you to know and be prepared and warn the body so that you all can pray.

00:21:52.439 --> 00:21:54.916
And some of it, people say, 'Well, can we change it?

00:21:54.916 --> 00:21:59.200
' Some of it we can, some we can't.

00:22:00.733 --> 00:22:07.120
And I'm going to say a lot of this we probably can't because I'm telling you, He's coming.

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:15.071
The sun is setting on this dispensation and where we are, and Jesus is getting ready to come back for His church.

00:22:19.345 --> 00:22:19.660
But I saw Adam's lease coming up.

00:22:23.140 --> 00:22:26.374
And I'll be real with y'all, I don't know where it's at in the Bible.

00:22:42.131 --> 00:22:49.253
I asked Him, 'Lord, show me,' and I've been trying to find where it talks about Adam's lease because He brought it up to me.

00:22:49.253 --> 00:22:54.840
And I said, 'Lord, where does it talk about that?

00:22:54.840 --> 00:22:58.935
' Because I'm telling you, I'm not a Bible scholar.

00:22:58.935 --> 00:23:19.046
I'm just getting these things from the Holy Spirit and I try to weigh it out with people who are educated in the Word, but I don't have a lot of people around me that are Bible scholars.

00:23:27.893 --> 00:23:28.207
But He talked to me about Adam's lease being up and I was like, 'Wow, Lord, this is interesting.

00:23:28.207 --> 00:23:34.940
' But He started talking to me about how everything was...

00:23:34.940 --> 00:23:44.320
I don't know, I'm not going to get into all that.

00:23:44.320 --> 00:23:50.220
I saw a lot about it and it was a wow.

00:24:05.444 --> 00:24:05.813
I talked to my wife about it, we talked about it, and I said, 'Babe, this is what the Lord said.

00:24:05.813 --> 00:24:15.559
' And the light was so strong when He appeared, it was so strong that it was brighter than the noonday sun at its fullest.

00:24:21.212 --> 00:24:21.390
The light that I saw when He appeared this way was so bright that I thought it was going to burn me up.

00:24:21.923 --> 00:24:25.960
And I said, 'Lord, you're going to have to turn it down or it's going to consume me.

00:24:25.960 --> 00:24:38.979
' And He took Himself behind the cliff of this thing and I could see the light—He shielded Himself with the light so that it would not burn me up in the spirit.

00:24:38.979 --> 00:24:53.018
It was so bright that it shielded, and the light was shining so bright on the other side of this shield that I could barely glimpse at it.

00:24:58.391 --> 00:25:02.893
But inside of this, this dove came out of that light and there was an olive branch in the dove's beak with the beautiful olive leaves on it.

00:25:06.679 --> 00:25:10.650
And it came out and it was flapping its wings coming out of that light, and it came over me.

00:25:10.650 --> 00:25:11.530
It was glory.

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:22.760
And what I'm trying to tell you all—I give you bits and pieces of things—but I'm trying to tell you all a little bit of something that He showed me.

00:25:28.271 --> 00:25:28.640
And we are out of time.

00:25:28.640 --> 00:25:31.800
Jesus is coming and you better get your house in order.

00:25:31.800 --> 00:25:38.920
It's time to get bold and on fire for God like you've never seen before.

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:44.720
It's time to arise and shine for the light has come.

00:25:44.720 --> 00:25:49.474
It's time for you to be serious about the Father's business, for He's coming.

00:25:49.474 --> 00:25:54.079
Are you ready for the soon return of the Lord Jesus Christ?

00:25:54.079 --> 00:26:03.787
For this dispensation of grace is coming to an end, ladies and gentlemen, and we're about to get ready to go into the seven years of tribulation.

00:26:19.039 --> 00:26:24.765
But the thousand-year reign—He has such a plan for each and every single one of you.

00:26:24.765 --> 00:26:35.627
We will see creative miracles, we will see blind eyes open, we will see dead men walk again, we will see the things that we've always desired to see.

00:26:35.627 --> 00:26:37.200
And thought, 'Is it possible?

00:26:37.200 --> 00:26:47.360
' But I'm trying to tell you all things are possible to him that believes, and a great move of the Spirit of God is right on us.

00:26:47.360 --> 00:26:48.320
It's right here.

00:26:51.040 --> 00:27:01.700
And I want my wife—she's here—to read some of the testimonies, just to stir you up, just to get you excited about what's coming, about the miracles that took place at Azusa Street.

00:27:01.700 --> 00:27:09.120
We've been reading that book, and I told her, 'Read it to me again, read it to me again.

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:14.430
' Because faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the Word of God.

00:27:24.893 --> 00:27:25.146
And this is not the Word of God, but this is something that God did in the past.

00:27:26.666 --> 00:27:36.520
And we read the Bible, but she reads these testimonies to me to show me, 'Brandon, it's happened once and He's going to do it again.

00:27:36.520 --> 00:27:40.204
' There is a great outpouring, a great harvest of souls.

00:27:41.824 --> 00:27:44.728
I'm telling you, He's the Lord of the harvest.

00:27:44.728 --> 00:27:54.560
'Hi everybody, I'm just reading a couple of miracles from the true stories of the miracles of Azusa Street...

00:27:55.480 --> 00:27:59.506
and there was—this is just one of the testimonies...

00:27:59.506 --> 00:28:06.735
these were just people that were there that God used to do healings and miracles.

00:28:06.735 --> 00:28:14.786
' And what we thought was cool, though, babe, was that a lot of these were young people.

00:28:14.786 --> 00:28:23.097
They were in the 18, 19, 12-year-olds—and 21-year-olds—but no, a lot of these people were not old people.

00:28:35.159 --> 00:28:35.399
They were all young people.

00:28:35.399 --> 00:28:41.359
I'm talking about being young Davids, being on fire with no fear.

00:28:52.045 --> 00:28:55.532
And I look back at what He did at Azusa, and we're reading—she's reading about—she goes, 'Brandon, another 18-year-old, another 21-year-old, another 12-year-old, another 15-year-old, 16-year-old was doing creative miracles, praying for people that needed a limb or eyes or whatever.

00:28:55.532 --> 00:29:04.280
' It wasn't like, 'Well, this guy was a seasoned veteran that was a preacher for 45 years at the Assemblies of God.

00:29:04.280 --> 00:29:07.709
' No, these were people that were just hungry, weren't they?

00:29:07.709 --> 00:29:18.575
Yeah, and it's exciting to hear these stories because you always think, 'Well, I have to be—well, I'm not a pastor, I'm not an evangelist, I can't be used.

00:29:18.575 --> 00:29:20.498
' He was using average Joes.

00:29:20.498 --> 00:29:21.720
He's going to use you.

00:29:21.720 --> 00:29:29.060
You don't have to have a platform; you don't have to have something huge.

00:29:29.060 --> 00:29:40.914
Now, I'm sorry to cut you off, baby, but I'm just—I have to tell everybody, it's not somebody that has a huge church.

00:29:40.914 --> 00:29:44.896
He's going to use you, ladies and gentlemen.

00:29:44.896 --> 00:29:46.655
He's going to use you.

00:29:52.834 --> 00:30:02.484
You could just be a stay-at-home mom that's just doing homework on the weekdays with their kids and—'Hey man, I made dinner for my family'—but God's going to use you.

00:30:10.720 --> 00:30:11.120
He doesn't have to look—you don't have to have a huge church.

00:30:11.120 --> 00:30:14.900
Most of these people who have huge churches, they have egos anyway.

00:30:14.900 --> 00:30:23.120
Look at it: 'Think of the movies The Elephant Man or Mask and you can picture the total disfigurement of this 25 to 30-year-old man who came to Azusa Street.

00:30:28.814 --> 00:30:30.159
He came there on his own, pathetically dragging his feet, sickening-looking, with one eye shooting up and the other looking down.

00:30:39.120 --> 00:30:39.375
His mind was perfectly fine, but he had been deformed and the condition grew worse and worse.

00:30:50.109 --> 00:30:50.324
He had been born deformed and the condition grew worse and worse.

00:30:50.754 --> 00:30:53.254
His mouth and jaw hung below his left breast.

00:30:53.254 --> 00:31:06.120
Mother Mangram made her way over'—this is one of the people that was there praying over people—'and made her way over to him, and he looked at her with his twisted eyes and uttered something.

00:31:06.120 --> 00:31:08.387
"What did you say?

00:31:08.387 --> 00:31:10.129
" asked Mother Mangram.

00:31:10.129 --> 00:31:13.393
He mumbled, "I came here to get healed.

00:31:13.393 --> 00:31:19.213
" She said, "Oh, praise God, you're going to have a great testimony.

00:31:19.213 --> 00:31:21.380
" He said, "Okay, I'm ready.

00:31:21.380 --> 00:31:25.310
" I love the fact that he came to Azusa ready.

00:31:25.310 --> 00:31:31.938
She slapped hands on him and held him there as his body danced under her touch.

00:31:46.693 --> 00:31:47.240
His face started contorting and coming back together.

00:31:47.240 --> 00:31:55.595
His jaw withdrew into place, his eyes rotated in their sockets, and his back, legs, and hands untwisted.

00:31:57.089 --> 00:31:57.271
I asked how long it took.

00:31:57.271 --> 00:32:03.427
She said a very attractive man stood in front of her in about five minutes.

00:32:03.427 --> 00:32:04.127
Praise God!

00:32:04.127 --> 00:32:07.093
Over two decades of deformity were made perfect in five minutes.

00:32:12.007 --> 00:32:12.253
I never found out his name.

00:32:12.253 --> 00:32:19.706
He became a minister after God blessed him with his healing.

00:32:32.034 --> 00:32:32.296
I believe this miracle alone could start an awakening.

00:32:32.296 --> 00:32:33.915
' It just takes one.

00:32:33.915 --> 00:32:37.535
I'm telling you all, wait until we start seeing this stuff.

00:32:37.535 --> 00:32:39.023
'Okay, here's another one.

00:32:39.023 --> 00:32:46.697
I asked if they remembered any specific miracles where God used Brother Seymour, and Sister Langford's eyes lit up.

00:32:46.697 --> 00:32:52.399
"I recall witnessing two of the greatest miracles where Seymour was powerfully used by God.

00:32:52.399 --> 00:32:53.840
" I was all ears.

00:32:53.840 --> 00:32:57.213
First, she told me about the man with the wooden leg.

00:32:57.213 --> 00:33:02.450
Seymour had approached a man with a wooden leg and asked, "What did you come here for?

00:33:05.973 --> 00:33:10.309
" The man replied, "I want you to pray for my leg; it's starting to get gangrene where the wooden leg attaches.

00:33:10.309 --> 00:33:15.400
" Seymour replied, "I'm just upset because you have the wooden leg on.

00:33:15.400 --> 00:33:23.559
It would be a challenge for God to grow a leg out with a wooden leg still attached.

00:33:28.773 --> 00:33:29.315
" The man removed the wooden leg and stood before Seymour, balancing on his one good leg.

00:33:29.315 --> 00:33:33.339
Seymour laid hands on the man and proclaimed, "Let Thy name be glorified.

00:33:33.339 --> 00:33:39.820
In the name of Jesus, I command this leg to grow out.

00:33:43.497 --> 00:33:46.290
The gangrene is gone; you are healed.

00:33:46.290 --> 00:33:48.091
" Seymour didn't preach that night.

00:33:55.824 --> 00:33:56.032
The miracle spoke for itself.

00:33:56.032 --> 00:33:57.927
Rejoicing was continuous; the crowd went wild.

00:34:06.874 --> 00:34:07.166
The man ran up the platform and around the room on two good legs.

00:34:07.166 --> 00:34:12.685
No one could get him to stop rejoicing and praising God.

00:34:12.685 --> 00:34:13.785
Praise God!

00:34:13.785 --> 00:34:17.679
Next, Sister Langford told of the man with no arm.

00:34:18.033 --> 00:34:22.639
He had lost his arm ten years earlier through a work-related accident.

00:34:30.279 --> 00:34:30.579
The arm had been totally severed at the shoulder.

00:34:30.579 --> 00:34:39.330
Brother Seymour asked the crowd, "Would you like to see God have a wonderful time here tonight?

00:34:39.330 --> 00:34:45.577
" Some of you may remember that man's leg that grew out about a year ago.

00:34:45.577 --> 00:34:52.690
Seymour then asked the one-armed man, "Can you work with just the one arm?

00:34:52.690 --> 00:35:01.696
" The man answered, "I'm just given the minimal paying jobs and I can barely make enough money to even eat.

00:35:01.696 --> 00:35:05.210
" Seymour shook his head and responded, "That's not good.

00:35:05.210 --> 00:35:06.110
Are you married?

00:35:06.110 --> 00:35:06.560
" "Yes.

00:35:10.310 --> 00:35:10.525
" "Got kids?

00:35:10.525 --> 00:35:10.954
" "Yes.

00:35:10.954 --> 00:35:15.269
" Seymour declared, "This man needs to be able to make a living.

00:35:15.269 --> 00:35:20.194
This man needs to work, and he needs to be able to pay his tithe.

00:35:20.194 --> 00:35:24.152
Will you tithe if I pray for you and God gives you your arm back?

00:35:24.152 --> 00:35:25.144
" Seymour asked teasingly.

00:35:25.144 --> 00:35:27.011
"Yes," the man replied.

00:35:27.011 --> 00:35:29.086
Seymour burst out laughing.

00:35:40.806 --> 00:35:41.097
"I'm just having fun.

00:35:41.097 --> 00:35:50.617
" Then he slapped his hands on the shoulder itself and commanded the arm to grow out.

00:35:50.617 --> 00:35:54.380
Almost instantly, it grew out.

00:36:04.640 --> 00:36:06.800
The healed man stood in total shock, then started moving his new arm and inspecting it with his other hand, wonder-struck by the miracle.

00:36:06.800 --> 00:36:19.460
A few weeks later, the man came back, bringing about two hundred people with him, telling many at the meeting that he had gotten his old job back.

00:36:19.460 --> 00:36:32.480
Many of those that he brought with him needed healing and left that evening fully restored as people in the crowd prayed and laid hands on each of them.

00:36:32.480 --> 00:36:33.970
' Okay, pause.

00:36:33.970 --> 00:36:35.049
Do you not see that?

00:36:35.049 --> 00:36:54.820
So he brought 200 people back, his arm grew out—everybody saw and knew who this was, this man whose arm was gone—and 200 people came to give their hearts to Jesus Christ.

00:37:00.373 --> 00:37:00.559
It's the goodness of God that brings men into repentance.

00:37:12.623 --> 00:37:13.074
Look at what's going to happen.

00:37:13.074 --> 00:37:23.219
There will be a great shaking to awaken, but in this, there will be a great harvest of souls.

00:37:23.219 --> 00:37:37.580
I'm telling you, when we start seeing things like this, we won't be able to keep the people away from church because they're going to be so hungry.

00:37:39.130 --> 00:37:40.932
People are broken out there; they're wanting a touch from Jesus.

00:37:40.932 --> 00:37:51.190
And when we start operating and walking in these demonstrations and manifestations of His glory, the people are going to come in by the groves.

00:37:51.190 --> 00:37:52.804
You have one more?

00:37:52.804 --> 00:37:57.844
'Yeah, this following miracle took healing out to a brand new level for me.

00:37:57.844 --> 00:38:03.040
I guarantee you ask anybody today and they'd all agree that Down syndrome...

00:38:03.040 --> 00:38:04.231
can't be healed.

00:38:04.231 --> 00:38:11.004
Most people would say that, but Sister Dundy would tell you differently if she were here.

00:38:11.004 --> 00:38:22.599
She prayed for maybe two dozen of those who were healed from this disorder, and I was lucky enough to meet one of them.

00:38:22.599 --> 00:38:31.549
I don't remember his name, but he was a little old man by the time I met him.

00:38:31.549 --> 00:38:40.306
His face had all the characteristics of someone who has Down syndrome, but he acted completely normal after God touched him through the prayers of Sister Dundy.

00:38:40.306 --> 00:38:45.599
He grew up and became a professor of music and taught in a California university.

00:38:45.599 --> 00:38:48.660
Sister Dundy remembered the day he was healed.

00:39:00.070 --> 00:39:00.245
He looked at her and said, "You're not Jesus.

00:39:00.245 --> 00:39:04.133
" She smiled and the mother explained to him that he's fine now.

00:39:12.098 --> 00:39:12.596
Of course, the mother couldn't talk; she was shaking her head in disbelief and crying—her son was just healed of Down syndrome.

00:39:14.163 --> 00:39:14.359
The next story surprised me even more.

00:39:15.457 --> 00:39:16.993
I still marvel when I think of it.

00:39:16.993 --> 00:39:23.131
One day, Sister Dundy found a horribly disfigured child around five years old amongst all the people at Azusa Street.

00:39:23.131 --> 00:39:26.070
He had scars all around his head.

00:39:26.070 --> 00:39:39.040
His family said that doctors literally had to piece his face back together after he fell from a staircase onto a concrete floor when he was about two and a half years old.

00:39:49.480 --> 00:39:49.653
The side of his face that took the impact was about one-quarter of an inch lower than the rest of his head.

00:39:49.653 --> 00:39:52.325
Sister Dundy could tell he wasn't normal mentally either.

00:39:52.325 --> 00:39:53.480
Her reaction: "Oh, how marvelous.

00:39:53.480 --> 00:39:57.096
God gets glory when things like this happen.

00:39:57.096 --> 00:40:00.113
" The father asked, "Things like what?

00:40:00.113 --> 00:40:02.290
" "He's going to be healed," she declared.

00:40:02.290 --> 00:40:06.251
See, by this time they didn't say, "God will," they said, "He is healed.

00:40:07.382 --> 00:40:11.830
" They had so much confidence that God was going to heal everyone and everything.

00:40:11.830 --> 00:40:18.760
"Let me hold the boy in my lap," she said as she sat him down and laid her hand on his head.

00:40:18.760 --> 00:40:24.005
Sister Dundy said she could see and feel her hand moving and shifting as she was praying.

00:40:24.005 --> 00:40:28.870
Finally, she took her hand away and the boy's face was perfectly normal.

00:40:35.564 --> 00:40:35.862
He was healed mentally as well.

00:40:35.862 --> 00:40:41.620
Now here's the shocker: this disfigured child grew up to be a handsome Hollywood star.

00:40:41.620 --> 00:40:43.008
His name was Robert Montgomery.

00:40:43.008 --> 00:40:46.974
He became an actor on stage and on screen as well as a director.

00:40:46.974 --> 00:40:51.615
In 1937, he was nominated for an Academy Award for best actor for a thriller called Night Must Fall.

00:40:51.615 --> 00:40:55.977
His daughter, Elizabeth Montgomery, starred in the hit TV show Bewitched in the 1960s.

00:41:12.536 --> 00:41:12.713
From grotesque disfigurement to a golden boy in Hollywood—how's that for a miracle?

00:41:12.713 --> 00:41:13.422
' That's amazing.

00:41:14.615 --> 00:41:18.390
I don't know if he ever gave God glory for it, but it's still amazing.

00:41:22.280 --> 00:41:22.730
You know, it even shows there that his daughter was doing a witchcraft show.

00:41:27.160 --> 00:41:27.440
I mean, but it wasn't about that—it's about God's goodness regardless.

00:41:27.440 --> 00:41:28.333
God is merciful.

00:41:28.333 --> 00:41:35.884
Now, what he did with it is his business, but God still loves you, and even whenever you mess up, He isn't holding it over your head.

00:41:35.884 --> 00:41:37.025
It's free will.

00:41:37.025 --> 00:41:41.180
You're able to operate and do whatever you want to do.

00:41:41.180 --> 00:41:44.173
Do you serve God because you love Him?

00:41:44.173 --> 00:41:48.988
Whenever He does something good for you, are you still going to love on Him?

00:41:52.359 --> 00:42:00.587
That man—I don't know if he did or not—He still did a creative miracle in his life, but it had nothing to do with his works.

00:42:00.587 --> 00:42:05.750
It had everything to do with just God's goodness.

00:42:05.750 --> 00:42:13.827
God's goodness is here, ladies and gentlemen, and I'm telling you, He saved you by grace through faith.

00:42:25.160 --> 00:42:25.465
It wasn't about any works, lest any man should boast.

00:42:30.187 --> 00:42:30.440
It has everything to do just with the fact that He loves you.

00:42:30.440 --> 00:42:34.200
Jesus Christ died for you when we were just sinners.

00:42:41.880 --> 00:42:43.249
All of us deserve hell, but He paid the price for you to not have to go to hell.

00:42:53.040 --> 00:42:53.440
He paid the price for your healing in your body.

00:42:53.440 --> 00:42:58.048
He took it all by grace.

00:42:58.048 --> 00:43:03.200
Everything we need is at the foot of the cross.

00:43:03.200 --> 00:43:11.600
He told me, He said, 'Brandon, I want you to walk in victory in your mental, emotional, physical, and financial life.

00:43:11.600 --> 00:43:19.326
' Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:43:19.326 --> 00:43:24.040
As it is in heaven, so let it be on earth.

00:43:24.040 --> 00:43:28.949
He wants it to be heaven on Earth.

00:43:28.949 --> 00:43:29.794
Boom!

00:43:29.794 --> 00:43:39.640
And I'm telling you, where we are in that time frame, people can focus on—I told you all, it's going to be like a quarter.

00:43:39.640 --> 00:43:48.969
You've got a quarter: the dark's going to be on one side and the light's going to be on the other.

00:43:48.969 --> 00:43:56.710
But it's your choice what side of the quarter you look at on a day-to-day basis.

00:43:56.710 --> 00:44:03.229
Dark's going to get darker and gross darkness, it's going to get very dark.

00:44:13.192 --> 00:44:13.464
But the light is going to get brighter and brighter as we keep walking with Him, taking the land for Jesus until He comes and gets us.

00:44:13.464 --> 00:44:14.955
Occupy until He comes.

00:44:14.955 --> 00:44:20.040
People say, 'Are you looking for Him to come back this Rosh Hashanah?

00:44:20.040 --> 00:44:23.599
' No, I want to occupy until He comes.

00:44:23.599 --> 00:44:26.048
When He comes back, that's on Him.

00:44:26.048 --> 00:44:32.520
Every day I want to occupy, take the land for Him, and when He says 'Come up,' then we're done.

00:44:37.914 --> 00:44:38.343
But until then, we've got a war to fight.

00:44:40.300 --> 00:44:41.596
But it's never for us to cower down in defeat.

00:44:41.596 --> 00:44:47.509
He paid the price for you to walk in victory in every area of your life.

00:44:47.509 --> 00:44:49.000
Praise God!

00:44:49.000 --> 00:44:53.150
Spiritually, physically, financially—everything, He paid the price.

00:44:54.425 --> 00:45:00.340
And it's by grace you receive it.

00:45:02.565 --> 00:45:06.800
You didn't earn it, you don't deserve it, it's by grace.

00:45:06.800 --> 00:45:10.085
But we walk out our salvation with fear and trembling.

00:45:10.085 --> 00:45:18.140
We seek Him daily and we don't open the doors for the devil to come and rob us.

00:45:18.140 --> 00:45:21.435
We walk by faith and not by sight.

00:45:21.435 --> 00:45:30.751
I'm not moved by what I see, I'm not moved by what I feel; I'm moved by what the Word of God says.

00:45:38.400 --> 00:45:38.920
And anything the Bible says we can have, we can have it.

00:45:46.466 --> 00:45:46.768
And it's time to get excited about it.

00:45:46.768 --> 00:45:50.555
Expectation brings the manifestation of what you've been believing for.

00:46:00.200 --> 00:46:00.627
And I saw an open door with great glory shining on the cracks, and He said, 'Brandon, that door is going to open.

00:46:07.410 --> 00:46:07.855
In a 24-hour period, everything is going to change.

00:46:07.855 --> 00:46:11.1000
' Watch what God is about to do.

00:46:12.640 --> 00:46:23.102
And if you're believing for the seeds you've sowed—there's a lot of people who say, 'I've sowed and sowed, and I've never seen the full manifestation.

00:46:23.102 --> 00:46:29.146
' I'm telling you, there will be decamillionaires in a matter of just a 24-hour period.

00:46:29.146 --> 00:46:40.105
There's going to be a great harvest if you're listening to Him and you're not allowing money to change you—you don't have a lust after money.

00:46:40.105 --> 00:46:42.490
God can trust you with it.

00:46:47.514 --> 00:46:47.823
I don't care that you have it as long as it doesn't have you.

00:46:47.823 --> 00:46:49.827
Money is a tool.

00:46:53.510 --> 00:46:57.080
And God wants you to be blessed in the city and in the field, coming in and going out.

00:46:57.080 --> 00:47:00.065
But if you can't handle it, He isn't going to give it to you.

00:47:00.065 --> 00:47:08.160
I've seen people—you see these people that win the lottery and they're broke within a couple weeks because they don't know how to handle it and it destroys them.

00:47:08.160 --> 00:47:09.726
God doesn't want that.

00:47:09.726 --> 00:47:23.420
